snippet.title: রবীন্দ্র সংগীত - Rabindra Sangeet Traditional Folk Songs - Superhit Bengali Songs

localized.description:
0:00:01 - Aji Pronomi Tomare
0:07:23 - Khato Jato Khoti Jato
0:14:01 - Ogo Nadi Apanbege
0:18:14 - Aaj Khela Bhangar Khela
0:21:43 - Amar Hiya Majhe
0:26:02 - Amar Jibanapatra
0:29:54 - Anmona Anmona
0:33:10 - Bhara Thak Smritisudhay

Rabindranath Tagore's songs are a treat to listen to. The lyrics have deep meaning and the songs will certainly stir you up. Listen to this compilation of traditional folk songs by him and have a great time.
